headline: Globally Acclaimed Theater Show Come from Away Set for First Production at Sea on Cunard's Queen Elizabeth
summary: Cunard will bring Come from Away — the Tony Award and Oliver Award-winning show — to sea for the first time ever in an exclusive production in collaboration with Music Theatre International.
